Title: Together We Are Unstoppable
Description:
$n, you must tell Alexstrasza and Nozdormu what has happened.

Khadgar and I will meet you at the Seat of the Aspects momentarily.
ObjectivesText: Return to the Seat of the Aspects and inform Alexstrasza about what happened after the defeat of Raszageth in the Vault of the Incarnates.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return to Alexstrasza the Life-Binder at the Seat of the Aspects in Valdrakken.
